### Donate

{:.do.no_toc}
### Donate

Healthcare professionals are running short of N95 masks and there may be people have masks in excess or are not exposed to coronavirus.

They can come forward and donate it.

Donate the N95 mask or any other healthcare device/equipment/safety gear that can support the healthcare professionals. Go to your local hospital's website to check if they are accepting donations.
